{"pin":"BB00100","subcodes":[{"code":"BB00100","anchor":"","title":"Alfayn Munajat","first_line":"Praise be to God Who hath brought forth the heavens and earth by His command; then shall they who have believed in God and His signs be gathered unto their Lord. O God! Thou art God, Lord of the heavens and earth, Thou knowest all things, and naught in the heavens or earth remaineth concealed from Thee [3.5s]... ...Glory be to Thee, O God! Thou art the God Who hath existed before all things, Who will exist after all things and will last beyond all things… Verily Thou art the Lord of all created things","first_line_orig":"بسم الله الرحمن الرحیم. الحمد لله الذی ابدع السموات و الارض بامره ثم الذین آمنوا بالله و آیاته الی ربهم یحشرون اللهم انت الله رب السموات و الارض تعلم کل شیء و لا یخفی علیک شیئ فی السموات و الارض  ","language":"1","word_count":"1800","subjects":"@tests and trials; sacrifice and suffering, @predictions and prophecies, @love of God, @transcendence; unknowability of God","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/AHDA.pdf#page=472\"\u003eAHDA.458.14\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://www.loomofreality.org/sources/SRC.pdf#page=23\"\u003eSRC.072\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://www.loomofreality.org/sources/SRC.pdf#page=44\"\u003eSRC.190\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://www.loomofreality.org/sources/SRC.pdf#page=50\"\u003eSRC.202\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Roma